data.description: Appraised at $458K by a Certified Residential Appraiser. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath in East Orlando is ready to welcome its new owner. There have been many upgrades to this home, including a new AC system (2020), a new roof (2021), new garbage disposal (2022), and a new dishwasher and exterior house painting (2023), among others. The kitchen has granite countertops and stainless appliances. The yard is fenced in and includes a screened-in lanai to view the beautiful sunsets Orlando has to offer. Do not miss this opportunity to tour your future home!
